reviewText: Can't wait for it to come in Scott frost is a great player I hope to be as good as him one day

As a novice one pocket player I found this dvd vwry informative. The road stories were cool too.

Scott The Freezer Frost rules, in this look into the game and strategies of the world's best One pocket player. A colorful, informative ride. The DVD comes autographed by Scott himself!Banking With The Beard -- The Movie
